item.title: CVE-2018-8173|2024-08-05T06:46:13.516Z -- microsoft -- microsoft%20infopath
item.description: A remote code execution vulnerability exists in Microsoft InfoPath when the software fails to properly handle objects in memory, aka "Microsoft InfoPath Remote Code Execution Vulnerability." This affects Microsoft Infopath.
